  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "html": "当年台湾中学<span class=\"vocab\">地理<span class=\"tooltip\">dì lǐ — geography</span></span>课都像历史课，大陆地理内容都停留在1949年。各省<span class=\"vocab\">物产<span class=\"tooltip\">wù chǎn — local products</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">资源<span class=\"tooltip\">zī yuán — natural resources</span></span>、东北九省我们记得一清二楚。“钢都鞍山，煤都抚顺”，我总以为是东北最大的两座城市。 <button class=\"play-button\" onclick=\"togglePlay(this)\" data-audio=\"audio/ANSHAN1p1.mp3\">▶︎</button>"
    },
    {
      "html": "2006年的电影《姨妈的后现代生活》里，斯琴高娃<span class=\"vocab\">扮演<span class=\"tooltip\">bàn yǎn — to play (a role/character)</span></span>的叶如棠，<span class=\"vocab\">抛夫弃女<span class=\"tooltip\">pāo fū qì nǚ — abandon husband and daughter</span></span>从东北回上海，<span class=\"vocab\">自称<span class=\"tooltip\">zì chēng — call oneself</span></span>从美国洛杉矶回来，过着她单身而文艺的生活。后来因为伤病入院，不得不联系家属。她十几年不见的<span class=\"vocab\">粗俗<span class=\"tooltip\">cū sú — vulgar; coarse</span></span>女儿来到医院<span class=\"vocab\">询问<span class=\"tooltip\">xún wèn — inquire</span></span>，护士本来挺<span class=\"vocab\">冷漠<span class=\"tooltip\">lěng mò — indifferent; apathetic</span></span>，一听是叶女士女儿，<span class=\"vocab\">秒变<span class=\"tooltip\">miǎo biàn — change instantly</span></span>热情“回来哒？”赵薇一愣“洛杉矶？<span class=\"vocab\">俺<span class=\"tooltip\">ǎn — I; me (dialect)</span></span>是鞍山的！”护士马上明白过来，又变得一脸<span class=\"vocab\">鄙视<span class=\"tooltip\">bǐ shì — despise; look down on</span></span>。 <button class=\"play-button\" onclick=\"togglePlay(this)\" data-audio=\"audio/ANSHAN1p2.mp3\">▶︎</button>"
    }
  ],
